{"tid":1474415,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"紐西蘭準備撤僑","createTime":"2019-08-15T07:14:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T17:58:56.000Z","uid":33373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"89bd26d7c02b181e9d8281988a658499a8885880","tid":1474415,"uid":33373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:14:52.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕香港反送中活動持續延燒，傳出中國當局不滿局勢惡化，已陳兵邊境伺機而動，美國總統川普昨也在推特上爆料，中國政府「正調動部隊到香港邊境」，紐西蘭政府已著手制定撤僑計畫，以便在必要時撤離留港紐西蘭僑民。<br />\n據紐西蘭媒體龍頭《Newstalk ZB》報導，該媒體政治編輯索珀（Barry Soper）表示，中國當局準軍事部隊陳兵香港邊境僅30公里，已引發外界疑慮，加上香港特首林鄭月娥揚言，若持續縱容「暴力」行為，將把香港推向一條不歸路。<br />\n<br />\n隨著香港局勢恐進一步惡化，紐西蘭外交和貿易部（MFAT）已著手製定計劃，以便在必要時撤離滯留香港的紐西蘭僑民；報導指出，香港約有1萬名紐西蘭僑民。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/world/breakingnews/2885010\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Famp%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2885010&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdq6fvQnHzZYMiebojCBKDlo%3D&h=b58a8656\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Famp%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2885010&h=5f2011ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/world/breakingnews/2885010</a>"},{"pid":"15ebeb0b2ab6eccbfe9a3ddfe4e4ccec70ae6612","tid":1474415,"uid":274149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:16:47.000Z","msg":"換美金，放係屋企"},{"pid":"18229b0192bdf4e77532c7fa5c3e0a999a7c6e81","tid":1474415,"uid":297045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T17:58:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}